title: William Morris Golden Lily 1000 Piece Puzzle
description:
William Morris was an outstanding character of many talents, being an architect, writer, social campaigner, artist and, with his Kelmscott Press, an important figure of the Arts and Crafts movement. Many of us probably know him best, however, from his superb furnishings and textile designs, intricately weaving together natural motifs in a highly stylized two-dimensional fashion influenced by medieval conventions.

Now includes an A4 poster for reference.
  • Dimensions: Box 10.00 x 10.00 in, Finished 29 x 20 in.
  • Size: 1000 pieces
